snippet.title: Tales of ARISE - [Blue Moon] by Ayaka - Song Trailer
snippet.description:
The thrilling story of Tales of Arise wouldn't be the same without incredible music.

Listen to the mesmerizing song Blue Moon, interpreted by Ayaka, and get ready to dive into your next big adventure on September 10.
🦉Pre-order now: www.talesofarise.com

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/talesofseries/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TalesofU
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/tales/
Web: https://www.bandainamcoent.eu

ESRB: TEEN  |  PEGI 12
#TalesofArise #BlueMoon #Ayaka
